Ok now there is only one more step to this tutorial for your fully working report system, and fortunatly for you it's
quite an easy one with two simple codes to add.

Open up your client class file and add this variable to the top where the other variables are;

[code]
public int reportTimer;[/code]

When you've added that locate your way to the "Boolean process" and add this under it;
[code]
if (reportTimer > 0) { 
	reportTimer--; 
} [/code]

For the record we are not using eventmanager as this is only a small code and there is no real point adding it 
as no real harm will be done.

[u][b]Known Bugs[/u]:

[*]Fortunatly for this server there is only one bug we know of, this bug is that sometimes,
when you open up the report-abuse interface and click it, your character may walk to the place you click on.

